Use the standard library
This is how to get_odd_collatz of n:
   Remember that result is []
   Do this n times:
      When remainder of n and 2 is 1, then:
         Add result to n
      End when
      When n is 1, then:
         Leave the loop
      End when
      When remainder of n and 2 is 0, then:
         Remember that n is quotient of n and 2
      But, if not:
         Remember that n is sum of (product of 3 and n) and 1
      End when
   End do
   Remember that i is 0
   Remember that reversed is []
   Do this result's length times:
      Add reversed to item (diff of (diff of result's length and 1) and i) in result
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is reversed
Now you know